  "message": "test(linalg): lock pinv_2x2 and matrix_power boundary parity\n\nAdded 10 differential goldens for two thin linalg ops (each had \u22642\ncases; avoided lstsq/eigvals/tensorsolve which are cod's active area):\n\n- pinv_2x2 (4 new): identity\u2192identity, diagonal\u2192reciprocal\n  (0.5, 0.25), rank-one-singular [[1,2],[2,4]] minimum-norm\n  [0.04, 0.08, 0.08, 0.16], zero-matrix\u2192zero-pinv\n- matrix_power (6 new): A^0 must return I regardless of A,\n  A^1 returns self, 90\u00b0-rotation\u00b2 negates, 90\u00b0-rotation\u2074 cycles\n  back to I, diagonal^{-1} reciprocates, diagonal^{-2} squares\n  the inverse\n\n94 linalg_differential cases total (from 84).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
